<h1 id="introduction">Introduction</h1>
<h2 id="the-problem">The problem</h2>
<h3 id="the-problem-1">The Problem</h3>
<p>Despite rising production, food prices are higher and increasingly volatile…</p>
<p><img src="FAO-cereals-price-BEAMER" alt="image" /><br /></p>
<p>[label=crisis-consequences]</p>
<h3 id="and-its-consequences">…and its consequences</h3>
<ul>
<li><p>&lt;1&gt; More price uncertainty <span class="math"> ⇒ </span> increase in risk for farmers.</p></li>
<li><p>&lt;2&gt; Increase in hunger among poor net food buyers …</p>
<ul>
<li><p>&lt;2&gt; who account for 88% of rural and 97% of urban poor households.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>&lt;3&gt; More than 60 food riots in 30 different countries.</p></li>
</ul>
<p>&lt;3&gt;<span> <img src="pic-food-riots" alt="image" /> </span></p>
<p>[label=hunger-estimates]</p>
<h3 id="undernourished-people-in-the-world">Undernourished people in the world</h3>
<p>…causing more (?) people to suffer hunger…</p>
<p><embed src="fig-hunger-estimates.eps" /></p>
<p>[label=frame-riots]</p>
<h3 id="food-riots">Food riots</h3>
<p>…and in turn leading to increasing violence.</p>
<p><embed src="fig-Lagi-et-al-food-riots.eps" /></p>
<h2 id="food-reserves">Food reserves</h2>
<h3 id="food-reserve-as-a-solution">Food reserve as a solution?</h3>
<p>If a poor grain-importing country decides to operate a grain reserve to stabilize prices…</p>
<ul>
<li><p>what is the ultimate target: welfare vs. hunger</p></li>
<li><p>what is the optimal size of the reserve?</p></li>
<li><p>is it better to use a financial asset?</p></li>
<li></li>
</ul>
<p><img src="pic-silos2" alt="image" /></p>
<h3 id="motivation-is-grain-storage-a-good-idea">Motivation: Is grain storage a good idea?</h3>
<p>The logic behind grain storage is simple:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>&lt;1-3&gt; Seven years of abundance followed by seven years of famine…</p></li>
<li><p>&lt;2-3&gt; What if country never has years of abundance?</p></li>
<li><p>&lt;3&gt; Opportunity cost of storing grain is very high!</p></li>
</ul>
<p>&lt;4-&gt;<span>To answer this, a model should quantify </span></p>
<ul>
<li><p>&lt;5-&gt; the increase on national hunger induced by an international crisis;</p></li>
<li><p>&lt;6-&gt; to what extent a reserve alleviates this increase, and at .</p></li>
</ul>
