<h3 id="possible-causes-of-high-food-prices">Possible causes of high food prices</h3>
<p>Affecting supply:</p>
<ol>
<li><p>rising oil prices;</p></li>
<li><p>declining stocks and reserves;</p></li>
<li><p>regional catastrophic weather;</p></li>
<li><p>export restrictions;</p></li>
<li><p>decline in productivity and R&amp;D in agriculture.</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Affecting demand:</p>
<ol>
<li><p>strong income growth in China and India;</p></li>
<li><p>biofuel production in the USA and Europe;</p></li>
<li><p>preventive imports surges;</p></li>
<li><p>speculation in financial markets.</p></li>
</ol>
